layout.js :: it is entry point of the next app every components of app render with this file
page.js :: it is a home page of the next app

there are two types of rendering takes place in next app
1.server side
2.client side 

every component lies within app directory by default a server side component(never use dynamic components like useState hook on server side component)
to make component clien side add 'use client' on the top of the code to make it client side
